  Locus:
    Page: 357
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Peace/Harmony
---
Peace is in that heart in which no wave of desire of any kind
arises. ... This eternal peace is your real existence -- it is not a state
or truth to be attained but to be realized; because you are ever That.
